OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,FA woman whose ex-partner secretly
OL,7,Ffilmed her using a camera hidden in a
OL,8,Fcharging plug says she is still
OL,9,Fanxious about being covertly filmed.
OL,11,FAngel, who has waived her legal right
OL,12,Fto anonymity but asked only to use her
OL,13,Fforename, was spied on by 42-year-old
OL,14,FStuart Morgan at a house in South
OL,15,FYorkshire using a pinhole camera.
OL,17,FHe gathered more than 300 images of
OL,18,Fher over the course of several months.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
