FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,FMorgan, who no longer lives in the UK,
OL,7,Fwas given a suspended sentence in
OL,8,FMarch this year and added to the Sex
OL,9,FOffenders register after pleading
OL,10,Fguilty to voyeurism at Sheffield Crown
OL,11,FCourt.
OL,13,FAngel has now spoken out about the
OL,14,Fimpact of his offending, as pressure
OL,15,Fmounts on the government to revise
OL,16,Flaws around access to covert recording
OL,17,Fequipment and the rules around filming
OL,18,Fwomen in public.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
