FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV Calendar,
OL,7,Fshe said: "I just felt like I was
OL,8,Fbeing watched - everything I did. Even
OL,9,Fin my own home when I was trying to
OL,10,Fshower."
OL,12,FAngel had been completely unaware she
OL,13,Fhad been filmed until she was sent a
OL,14,Fstill from one of the recordings at
OL,15,Fthe end of her relationship wth Morgan.
OL,17,FIt later transpired he had hundreds of
OL,18,Fimages of her - many of which she
OL,19,Fworries may have been shared with
OL,20,Fothers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,F"At the time when I left, I knew there
OL,7,Fwas one picture. I didn't know about
OL,8,Fthe hundreds of pictures until a year
OL,9,Fand a half later," she said.
OL,11,F"I felt very worried. I felt like I
OL,12,Fwas being watched everywhere I went. I
OL,13,Ffelt quite humiliated as well, because
OL,14,Fthe ones where I was asleep he was
OL,15,Fpositioning himself in certain places.
OL,17,F"It's seeped into all aspects of my
OL,18,Flife. Because it was so covert that it
OL,19,Fmakes me wonder, 'is there something
OL,20,Fhidden, is that person recording me?'
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,F"Everyone walks around with a phone.
OL,7,FThe lens is on the back of it, so even
OL,8,Fif somebody's just looking at their
OL,9,Fphone, sometimes I feel like, 'are
OL,10,Fthey recording me? Are they sending
OL,11,Fphotos to him?'
OL,13,F"It even affected me with things like
OL,14,Fshowering, because I didn't want to be
OL,15,Fnaked."
OL,17,F'We brush it off'
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
