PN,33206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,FIn recent years, there has been
OL,7,Fgrowing pressure for crimes like
OL,8,Fvoyeurism and public indecency to be
OL,9,Ftaken more seriously.
OL,11,FA law introduced in 2019 saw
OL,12,Fupskirting classed as a criminal
OL,13,Foffence, while the murder of Sarah
OL,14,FEverard highlighted how criminals like
OL,15,FWayne Couzens - who had been
OL,16,Fidentified in a case of indecent
OL,17,Fexposure days earlier - can escalate
OL,18,Ftheir behaviour.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
