PN,33207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,FLisa Squire's daughter, Libby, was
OL,7,Fraped and murdered by Pawel Relowicz
OL,8,Fin Hull in 2019 while she was walking
OL,9,Fhome from a nightclub in the city.
OL,11,FIn the months before, Relowicz had
OL,12,Fbeen caught spying on women in their
OL,13,Fhomes, stealing intimate items from
OL,14,Fthem and committing indecent acts in
OL,15,Fpublic.
OL,17,FSince then, Lisa has committed to
OL,18,Fcampaigning for more people to report
OL,19,Fnon-contact sexual offences as part of
OL,20,Fthe It Does Matter campaign.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,F"They are serious offences and they
OL,7,Fcan escalate," she said. "Not all non-
OL,8,Fcontact sexual offenders will go on to
OL,9,Fescalate. But those who do, escalate
OL,10,Fto serious sexual assaults, rape or
OL,11,Fmurder, like in my daughter's case.
OL,13,F"I know lots of women who have been
OL,14,Fvictim of a non-contact sexual
OL,15,Foffence, and we brush it off.
OL,17,F"If what happened to the girls who
OL,18,F(Relowicz) offended against before he
OL,19,Fkilled Libby happened today, I'd like
OL,20,Fto think they would be taken more
OL,21,Fseriously."
OL,26,@zD@ApmzD@Jpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,FThe sentiment was echoed by Angel, who
OL,7,Fsaid: "I think it's quite a dangerous
OL,8,Fthing to see it as a low-level offence.
OL,10,F"Often, as was in my case, it wasn't a
OL,11,Fstandalone behaviour. It was part of a
OL,12,Fwider pattern of control. People who
OL,13,Fdo those behaviours often escalate to
OL,14,Fsomething much more dangerous. They
OL,15,Fvery rarely de-escalate.
OL,17,F"I think that seeing it as a low-level
OL,18,Foffence makes it feel like it's okay."
OL,20,FWhat does the law say?
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
