PN,33210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,FDevices with inbuilt recording
OL,7,Fequipment, like charging plugs,
OL,8,Fclocks, WiFi hubs, car keys and smoke
OL,9,Falarms, can be bought cheaply online.
OL,11,FThe use of hidden cameras in England
OL,12,Fand Wales is legal, unless being used
OL,13,Fto film private acts or in spaces
OL,14,Fwhere the subject would have an
OL,15,Fexpectation of privacy.
OL,17,FCovertly recording someone without
OL,18,Ftheir knowledge for sexual
OL,19,Fgratification or to cause distress is
OL,20,Fa criminal offence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
