PN,33211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,FThe law prohibits non-consensual
OL,7,Ffilming of private acts, upskirting,
OL,8,Fand distributing intimate images.
OL,10,FVoyeurism and upskirting can result in
OL,11,Fup to two years in custody.
OL,13,FIn April, a 33-year-old man in
OL,14,FNorthamptonshire was jailed for
OL,15,Fsecretly filming several women over a
OL,16,F10-year period using cameras disguised
OL,17,Fas pens, USB sticks and plugs.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
