FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1781892673
OL,3,CWoman filmed by camera hidden in
OL,4,Ccharger 'humiliated'
OL,6,FA man in the Isle of Wight was last
OL,7,Fyear sentenced after he hid a camera
OL,8,Finside an air freshener to spy on a
OL,9,Fwoman.
OL,11,F"I don't see any legitimate reason for
OL,12,Fthat device existing," Angel said.
OL,13,F"I've tried to think what someone
OL,14,Fcould need that for and there's
OL,15,Fnothing. If you're filming someone,
OL,16,Fpeople should know about that."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/12
